It is enacted by the General Assembly as follows:
1 SECTION 1. Sections 23-18.18-3 and 23-18.18-5 of the General Laws in Chapter 23-18.18
2 entitled "Consumer PFAS Ban Act of 2024." are hereby amended to read as follows:
